These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: mango, pepper, pomegranate, raspberry
4 different games are played: billiard, bridge, go, scrabble
1. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
2. the person eating mango is the person playing scrabble##1
3. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
4. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
5. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | raspberry | pomegranate | pepper | mango   |
| Game   | bridge  | billiard     | go   | scrabble |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, cooking, video-games, woodworking
4 different games are played: billiard, whist, snooker, bridge
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person playing whist##1
2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
5. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby   | video-games | woodworking | cooking | camping    |
| Game   | snooker    | whist      | billiard | bridge |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, dutch, chinese, japanese
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, drama, mystery, time-travel
1. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
2. the argentine is the person watching crime movies##1
3. the person watching drama movies is on the far right##1
4. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the japanese##1
5. the chinese is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Nationality         | argentine | japanese | chinese   | dutch |
| Movie-Genre   | crime   | mystery | time-travel | drama         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, september, november, april
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, sailing, surfing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Birthday   | april | september | august  | november      |
| Sport         | sailing | tennis   | surfing | basketball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
There 4 different types of food: cauliflower, cucumber, kiwi, pineapple
4 different games are played: billiard, mah-jongg, poker, domino
1. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
2. the person playing poker is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
3. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person playing domino##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing poker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Food   | pineapple | kiwi | cucumber | cauliflower |
| Game    | billiard       | domino | poker | mah-jongg     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, apricot, grapes, cauliflower
4 different pets are kept: fish, frog, goldfish, mouse
1. the person eating apricot is on the far right##1
2. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
4. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
5. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | cauliflower | grapes | asparagus | apricot |
| Pet           | fish      | goldfish | mouse | frog    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, electronic, indie, salsa
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, mechanic, writer, security-guard
1. the writer is on the far left##1
2. the fan of salsa is on the far right##1
3. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
4. the mechanic is on the far right##1
5. the fan of electronic is on the left of the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Music-Genre   | indie | electronic | classical | salsa  |
| Job           | writer | accountant | security-guard       | mechanic |

