.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
4 different games are played: whist, scrabble, monopoly, billiard
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, quad-bike, tram, trike
1. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
2. the person driving the trike is the person playing billiard##1
3. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing whist##1
4. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
5. the person driving the car is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Game         | monopoly | whist      | scrabble | billiard |
| Transport   | car          | quad-bike | tram     | trike    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-9::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, fantasy, spy, zombie
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: siglo, bluemaster, dunhill, pall-mall
1. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
2. the person watching family movies is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
3. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1
4. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
5. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | spy       | family | zombie   |
| Cigar     | bluemaster | dunhill | pall-mall   | siglo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, milk, sprite
House: futuristic, farmhouse, gothic-revival, colonial
1. the futuristic house is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
3. the colonial house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
4. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Beverage    | cola | milk  | hot-chocolate | sprite |
| House   | colonial | gothic-revival | farmhouse          | futuristic    |

