.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, milk, sprite, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, gardening, dancing, sudoku
1. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking milk is the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Beverage      | sprite | milk  | hot-chocolate | water |
| Hobby   | camping  | dancing | sudoku           | gardening   |

