3. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
4. the argentine is on the right of the canadian##1
5. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Nationality   | canadian | argentine | thai | dutch  |
| Cigar           | baccarat | cain      | fonseca | ritmeester |

