.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, sprite, water
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, lime, spinach, pumpkin
1. the person eating pumpkin is the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person eating lime is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person drinking sprite is the person eating spinach##1
4. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person eating lime##1
5. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Beverage   | sprite | juice  | coffee | water   |
| Food        | spinach | lime | pumpkin    | grapefruit |

