.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-14::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, bus, boat, airplane
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, fantasy, horror, thriller
1. the person driving the roller is the person watching fantasy movies##1
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
3. the person driving the bus is the person watching horror movies##1
4. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
5. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |     4      |
| Transport          | roller | boat  | bus  | airplane |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy   | comedy | horror | thriller   |

