.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-15::.
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, egyptian, japanese, malaysian
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, blue, purple, orange
1. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
2. the person who likes orange is on the far left##1
3. the egyptian is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
4. the person who likes orange is on the left of the malaysian##1
5. the person who likes purple is on the right of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | japanese | malaysian     | argentine | egyptian |
| Color         | orange | blue | lavender   | purple   |

