.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-17::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, epic, horror, western
House: art-deco, modern, cape-cod, cottage
1. the cottage house is the person watching horror movies##1
2. the person watching comedy movies is the modern house##1
3. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
5. the cottage house is on the right of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |    3    |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic      | horror | western | comedy |
| House     | art-deco | cottage    | cape-cod  | modern |

