.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-19::.
City: miami, edinburgh, san-francisco, colone
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, drama, scientific, spy
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
2. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
3. the person watching scientific movies is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
4. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
5. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
| City         | edinburgh | san-francisco | colone | miami |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | scientific    | action      | drama   |

